title: Peace Out!
description: Shaun Burns doing what he does best – hunting down waves along California's Central Coast drawing smooth lines, laying it on rail, and stomping airs. As his college career is quickly coming to an end, it's time to say "peace out" to college and hello to whatever comes next.
